Edinburgh NPT Network - 3km Demo Data

NPT_demo_3km.Rd

This data set contains network data for Edinburgh within a 3km radius, sourced from NPT. It highlights specific network characteristics important for transportation planning.

Usage

NPT_demo_3km

Format

An object of class sf (inherits from data.frame).

Examples

data(NPT_demo_3km)
